&lt;h1 id="validators">Validators&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>The validator view display active validators and their current status.
The information displayed is&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Moniker and address&lt;/li>
&lt;li>MissedBlocks : How many blocks missed in slashing window&lt;/li>
&lt;li>CCF : Checks if validator is on the Cardano ChainFollower list&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Tokens: How many delegated tokens&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Power: Voting power&lt;/li>
&lt;li>State: Signing state&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Commission: Commission rate set on this validator&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;figure class="card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4" style="max-width: 910px">
